## Runtime Safety Enforcement (CRITICAL)

- Supabase-like results: const items = data ?? []
- Array operation guards: (items ?? []).map(...); Array.isArray(items) ? items.map(...) : []
- React state: useState<Type[]>([])
- API shapes: const list = Array.isArray(response?.data) ? response.data : []
- Optional chaining: obj?.property?.nested
- Destructuring defaults: const { items = [], count = 0 } = response ?? {}

